{"title":"SpringBoot入门","slug":"SpringBoot入门","date":"2021-08-03T15:32:14.000Z","updated":"2021-08-08T06:03:57.205Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/SpringBoot入门.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"springboot\">SpringBoot</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p><strong>自动装配</strong></p></li>\r\n<li><p><strong>约定大于配置</strong></p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"微服务\">微服务</h3>\r\n<p>是一种架构。打破all-in-one</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"第一个springboot\">第一个SpringBoot</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>jdk1.8</li>\r\n<li>maven</li>\r\n<li>SpringBoot</li>\r\n<li>IDEA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>官方提供快速生成网站，IDEA集成了。</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://start.spring.io/\">Spring Initializr</a></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"官网创建\">官网创建</h3>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804092417019.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804092417019\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804092417019</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"idea创建\">IDEA创建</h3>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804094858227.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804094858227\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804094858227</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804094920406.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804094920406\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804094920406</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"第一个springboot-web应用\">第一个SpringBoot WEB应用</h3>\r\n<p><strong>HelloController.java</strong></p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">package</span> top.huii.hellospringboot.controller;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.stereotype.Controller;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestMapping;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.ResponseBody;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@Controller</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RequestMapping(&quot;/hello&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">HelloController</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@GetMapping(&quot;h1&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@ResponseBody</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title function_\">hello</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;hello&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804100229247.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804100229247\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804100229247</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"彩蛋自定义banner\">彩蛋——自定义banner</h3>\r\n<p><a\r\nhref=\"https://www.bootschool.net/ascii-art\">Ascii艺术字实现个性化Spring\r\nBoot启动banner图案，轻松修改更换banner.txt文件内容，收集了丰富的banner艺术字和图，并且支持中文banner下载，让你的banner好玩儿更有意思。-bootschool.net</a></p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804095657702.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804095657702\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804095657702</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"原理初探\">原理初探</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"自动配置\">自动配置</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"pom.xml\">pom.xml</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>spring-boot-dependencies:核心依赖在父工程中</li>\r\n<li>在写或引入一些依赖，不需要指定版本</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"启动器\">启动器</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-test<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>SpringBoot启动场景</p></li>\r\n<li><p>会将所有的功能场景变成一个个的启动器</p></li>\r\n<li><p>我们要使用什么功能，就只需要找到对应的启动器就可以了</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"主程序\">主程序</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">package</span> top.huii.hellospringboot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.SpringBootApplication;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@SpringBootApplication</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">HelloSpringBootApplication</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title function_\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        SpringApplication.run(HelloSpringBootApplication.class, args);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"SpringBootApplication\">@SpringBootApplication</span></strong>表明是一个SpringBoot应用</li>\r\n<li>SpringBoot所有自动配置都是在启动的时候扫描并加载，但不一定生效，要判断条件是否成立，要导入对应的start就有对应的启动器。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"配置文件\">配置文件</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"yaml\">yaml</h4>\r\n<p>不推荐使用properties配置文件，推荐使用yaml</p>\r\n<p>yaml对空格要求极高</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">student:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"string\">HUII</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">age:</span> <span class=\"number\">12</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p>松散绑定：last-name等同于lastName</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"多环境切换\">多环境切换</h4>\r\n<p><strong>最外层配置优先级最高</strong></p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804112523629.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804112523629\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804112523629</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>使用yaml还能这样</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804112915370.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804112915370\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804112915370</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804113116314.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804113116314\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804113116314</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"web开发\">WEB开发</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"导入静态资源\">导入静态资源</h3>\r\n<p>在springboot下，可以使用一下方式处理静态资源</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>webjars http://127.0.0.1:8080/webjars</li>\r\n<li>public, static, /**, resources http://127.0.0.1:8080/</li>\r\n<li>优先级：resources&gt;static(默认)&gt;public</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210805114331640.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210805114331640\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210805114331640</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"thymeleaf模板引擎\">thymeleaf模板引擎</h3>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RequestMapping(&quot;test&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title function_\">test</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210805120835389.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210805120835389\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210805120835389</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210805120753277.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210805120753277\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210805120753277</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>语法。。。</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"常用注解\">常用注解</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"Controller\">@Controller</span></strong> 控制器</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"RequestMapping\">@RequestMapping</span>(value =\r\n\"/hello\")</strong> 设置路由</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"ResponseBody\">@ResponseBody</span></strong>\r\n直接返回字符串</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"RestController\">@RestController</span></strong>\r\n相当于@Controller + <span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"ResponseBody\">@ResponseBody</span>,返回json对象</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"GetMapping\">@GetMapping</span>(value = \"/hello\")</strong>\r\n相当于@RequestMapping(value = \"/hello\", method=RequestMethod.GET)\r\n只接受GET方法请求。方式不对会报405错误</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"PostMapping\">@PostMapping</span>(value = \"/hello\")</strong>\r\n相当于@RequestMapping(value = \"/hello\", method=RequestMethod.POST)\r\n只接受POST方法请求。</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"DeleteMapping\">@DeleteMapping</span>(value =\r\n\"/hello\")</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"PutMapping\">@PutMapping</span>(value =\r\n\"/hello\")</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"restful风格\">Restful风格</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RequestMapping(&quot;usr/&#123;id&#125;/&#123;name&#125;/&#123;pwd&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@ResponseBody</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> Object <span class=\"title function_\">user1</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"meta\">@PathVariable(&quot;id&quot;)</span> Integer id, <span class=\"meta\">@PathVariable(&quot;name&quot;)</span> String name, <span class=\"meta\">@PathVariable(&quot;pwd&quot;)</span> String pwd)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">User</span> <span class=\"variable\">user</span> <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"title class_\">User</span>(id, name, pwd);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> user;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210808104321466.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210808104321466\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210808104321466</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"redis\">Redis</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-data-redis<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"拦截器\">拦截器</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">UserInterceptor</span> <span class=\"keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"title class_\">HandlerInterceptor</span> &#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n","more":"<h2 id=\"springboot\">SpringBoot</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p><strong>自动装配</strong></p></li>\r\n<li><p><strong>约定大于配置</strong></p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"微服务\">微服务</h3>\r\n<p>是一种架构。打破all-in-one</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"第一个springboot\">第一个SpringBoot</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>jdk1.8</li>\r\n<li>maven</li>\r\n<li>SpringBoot</li>\r\n<li>IDEA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>官方提供快速生成网站，IDEA集成了。</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://start.spring.io/\">Spring Initializr</a></p>\r\n<h3 id=\"官网创建\">官网创建</h3>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804092417019.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804092417019\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804092417019</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"idea创建\">IDEA创建</h3>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804094858227.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804094858227\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804094858227</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804094920406.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804094920406\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804094920406</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"第一个springboot-web应用\">第一个SpringBoot WEB应用</h3>\r\n<p><strong>HelloController.java</strong></p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">package</span> top.huii.hellospringboot.controller;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.stereotype.Controller;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestMapping;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.ResponseBody;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@Controller</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RequestMapping(&quot;/hello&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">HelloController</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@GetMapping(&quot;h1&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"meta\">@ResponseBody</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title function_\">hello</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;hello&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804100229247.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804100229247\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804100229247</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"彩蛋自定义banner\">彩蛋——自定义banner</h3>\r\n<p><a\r\nhref=\"https://www.bootschool.net/ascii-art\">Ascii艺术字实现个性化Spring\r\nBoot启动banner图案，轻松修改更换banner.txt文件内容，收集了丰富的banner艺术字和图，并且支持中文banner下载，让你的banner好玩儿更有意思。-bootschool.net</a></p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804095657702.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804095657702\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804095657702</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"原理初探\">原理初探</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"自动配置\">自动配置</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"pom.xml\">pom.xml</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>spring-boot-dependencies:核心依赖在父工程中</li>\r\n<li>在写或引入一些依赖，不需要指定版本</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"启动器\">启动器</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-test<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>SpringBoot启动场景</p></li>\r\n<li><p>会将所有的功能场景变成一个个的启动器</p></li>\r\n<li><p>我们要使用什么功能，就只需要找到对应的启动器就可以了</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4 id=\"主程序\">主程序</h4>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">package</span> top.huii.hellospringboot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.SpringBootApplication;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@SpringBootApplication</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">HelloSpringBootApplication</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title function_\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        SpringApplication.run(HelloSpringBootApplication.class, args);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"SpringBootApplication\">@SpringBootApplication</span></strong>表明是一个SpringBoot应用</li>\r\n<li>SpringBoot所有自动配置都是在启动的时候扫描并加载，但不一定生效，要判断条件是否成立，要导入对应的start就有对应的启动器。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 id=\"配置文件\">配置文件</h3>\r\n<h4 id=\"yaml\">yaml</h4>\r\n<p>不推荐使用properties配置文件，推荐使用yaml</p>\r\n<p>yaml对空格要求极高</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">student:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"string\">HUII</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">age:</span> <span class=\"number\">12</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<p>松散绑定：last-name等同于lastName</p>\r\n<h4 id=\"多环境切换\">多环境切换</h4>\r\n<p><strong>最外层配置优先级最高</strong></p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804112523629.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804112523629\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804112523629</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>使用yaml还能这样</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804112915370.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804112915370\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804112915370</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210804113116314.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210804113116314\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210804113116314</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"web开发\">WEB开发</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"导入静态资源\">导入静态资源</h3>\r\n<p>在springboot下，可以使用一下方式处理静态资源</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>webjars http://127.0.0.1:8080/webjars</li>\r\n<li>public, static, /**, resources http://127.0.0.1:8080/</li>\r\n<li>优先级：resources&gt;static(默认)&gt;public</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210805114331640.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210805114331640\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210805114331640</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"thymeleaf模板引擎\">thymeleaf模板引擎</h3>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RequestMapping(&quot;test&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> String <span class=\"title function_\">test</span><span class=\"params\">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210805120835389.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210805120835389\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210805120835389</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210805120753277.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210805120753277\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210805120753277</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>语法。。。</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"常用注解\">常用注解</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"Controller\">@Controller</span></strong> 控制器</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"RequestMapping\">@RequestMapping</span>(value =\r\n\"/hello\")</strong> 设置路由</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"ResponseBody\">@ResponseBody</span></strong>\r\n直接返回字符串</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"RestController\">@RestController</span></strong>\r\n相当于@Controller + <span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"ResponseBody\">@ResponseBody</span>,返回json对象</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"GetMapping\">@GetMapping</span>(value = \"/hello\")</strong>\r\n相当于@RequestMapping(value = \"/hello\", method=RequestMethod.GET)\r\n只接受GET方法请求。方式不对会报405错误</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"PostMapping\">@PostMapping</span>(value = \"/hello\")</strong>\r\n相当于@RequestMapping(value = \"/hello\", method=RequestMethod.POST)\r\n只接受POST方法请求。</li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"DeleteMapping\">@DeleteMapping</span>(value =\r\n\"/hello\")</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"citation\"\r\ndata-cites=\"PutMapping\">@PutMapping</span>(value =\r\n\"/hello\")</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"restful风格\">Restful风格</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@RequestMapping(&quot;usr/&#123;id&#125;/&#123;name&#125;/&#123;pwd&#125;&quot;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">@ResponseBody</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> Object <span class=\"title function_\">user1</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"meta\">@PathVariable(&quot;id&quot;)</span> Integer id, <span class=\"meta\">@PathVariable(&quot;name&quot;)</span> String name, <span class=\"meta\">@PathVariable(&quot;pwd&quot;)</span> String pwd)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">User</span> <span class=\"variable\">user</span> <span class=\"operator\">=</span> <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"title class_\">User</span>(id, name, pwd);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> user;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210808104321466.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210808104321466\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210808104321466</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"redis\">Redis</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight xml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.boot<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>spring-boot-starter-data-redis<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<h2 id=\"拦截器\">拦截器</h2>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title class_\">UserInterceptor</span> <span class=\"keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"title class_\">HandlerInterceptor</span> &#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n","categories":[{"name":"Coding","path":"api/categories/Coding.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Spring","path":"api/tags/Spring.json"},{"name":"SpringBoot","path":"api/tags/SpringBoot.json"}]}